{"tid":436202,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"初戀對象係米最令人最難忘？","createTime":"2017-10-15T03:15:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T05:34:53.000Z","uid":146893,"like":12,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a69227b64c32c70480505cb91902bb72e6d213f8","tid":436202,"uid":146893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:15:09.000Z","msg":"你地仲記唔記得個初戀對象？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算分左手，都仲會掛住佢？<br />\n就算拍緊拖，都仲會諗起佢？<br />\n過左好多年，都仲忘記唔到？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我仲好記得，都間唔中會諗起佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一早唔記得，係你講起先記得"},{"pid":"af6cc90de5915e0ae5f616a9582404123de6a119","tid":436202,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:17:57.000Z","msg":"唔係"},{"pid":"39c60af75ba92649a4e3f00b73b250af7b201365","tid":436202,"uid":2263,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:19:45.000Z","msg":"米你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4f31c6a999d46e8165f28a8104b614e55490d5","tid":436202,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:27:34.000Z","msg":"後悔到仆街囉唔該"},{"pid":"552deb9df0f90e9aadebbae5186b89d278346a8d","tid":436202,"uid":129521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:32:19.000Z","msg":"係連登問？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一堆連登仔Strong hold緊個初戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41973d2acaaabdd04ab859adb3471a9dfcef4633","tid":436202,"uid":38958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T03:34:15.000Z","msg":"好想同初戀一齊番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最真摯既愛情"},{"pid":"7a89ddc9feed43cc77c4902b511844737270296e","tid":436202,"uid":2419,"like":